Judwaa is the story of twin girls who share the same face but have contrasting personalities and destinies. One is gentle and reserved, while the other is bold and fearless. As fate weaves unexpected twists, their lives take dramatic turns. Starring Aina Asif in a dual role, this gripping drama explores identity, destiny, and the power of choice.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Pahalgam Terror Attack ‡§ï‡•á ‡§µ‡•Ä‡§°‡§ø‡§Ø‡•ã ‡§Æ‡•á‡§Ç ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§¶‡•Ä‡§¶‡•ã‡§Ç ‡§®‡•á ‡§∞‡•ã‡§§‡•á-‡§∞‡•ã‡§§‡•á ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ó‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡§¶‡§¶, ‡§ï‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§¨‡•ã‡§≤‡•á? Kashmir Attack
snippet.description:
Gunmen opened fire at a group of tourists in Jammu and Kashmir's Pahalgam. A woman, who was an eyewitness to the attack, narrated the sequence of events as a gunman targeted her husband. The attack took place at around 2:30 pm on Tuesday afternoon when a group of terrorists, dressed in fatigues, opened fire on tourists in Pahalgam's Baisaran meadow. The person who died has been identified as Manjunath and is from Karnataka's Shivamogga.

localized.description:
Gunmen opened fire at a group of tourists in Jammu and Kashmir's Pahalgam. A woman, who was an eyewitness to the attack, narrated the sequence of events as a gunman targeted her husband. The attack took place at around 2:30 pm on Tuesday afternoon when a group of terrorists, dressed in fatigues, opened fire on tourists in Pahalgam's Baisaran meadow. The person who died has been identified as Manjunath and is from Karnataka's Shivamogga.

Simran has completed 30 years of being an actress in the industry and has gained respect and love from all over the world! At the JFW Movie Awards 2025, a grand celebration took place as Simran was honoured by more than 10 actresses such as Keerthy Suresh, Krithi Shetty, Parvathy Thiruvothu, Amala Paul, Sri Gouri Priya, Sriya Reddy, Nikhila VImal, Grace Antony, Swasika and Dushara! Simran's speech was bold as she talks about how she received an unnecessary text from a co-star and that she rather do "Aunty" roles than roles that do not mean anything! 

Simran recently did a cameo in the blockbuster hit "Good Bad Ugly" and was praised for her brilliant performance and her iconic dance was used in the movie with Ajith Kumar!

I was the first guest at Yuvraj Singh‚Äôs first-ever restaurant, Koca, in Gurugram ‚Äî and it wasn‚Äôt just about delicious food. This episode is packed with heartwarming, inspiring, and unheard stories straight from Yuvraj‚Äôs life.

I sat down for an intimate conversation with Yuvraj Singh and his mother, Shabnam Singh, where she opened up like never before. From adorable childhood memories of Yuvi, his rebellious streak, and the challenges of raising a champion, to their family‚Äôs struggle during his battle with cancer ‚Äî she shared it all.

We also spoke about Yuvraj‚Äôs journey to cricket stardom, his equation with his father Yograj Singh, her parenting style as a single mother, and for the first time, how she was introduced to her daughter-in-law Hazel Keech. It‚Äôs a candid, emotional and joyful episode you don‚Äôt want to miss!

And of course, you‚Äôll get an exclusive tour of Koca, where Yuvi takes me through his favorite dishes and the story behind launching his dream restaurant.

From the secret behind her legendary Kadhi Chawal, to Yuvraj‚Äôs most emotional cricket moments, his battle with cancer, love life with Hazel Keech and becoming a dad at 40, nothing is off the table!


Hit play, join us for this special brunch, and don‚Äôt forget to like, comment, and subscribe!

en-GB.description:
Join this channel to get access to Uncut & Behind The Scene Videos of your Favourite Celebs:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDnq05Q89oYq-Tz5boL73Tw/join

I was the first guest at Yuvraj Singh‚Äôs first-ever restaurant, Koca, in Gurugram ‚Äî and it wasn‚Äôt just about delicious food. This episode is packed with heartwarming, inspiring, and unheard stories straight from Yuvraj‚Äôs life.

I sat down for an intimate conversation with Yuvraj Singh and his mother, Shabnam Singh, where she opened up like never before. From adorable childhood memories of Yuvi, his rebellious streak, and the challenges of raising a champion, to their family‚Äôs struggle during his battle with cancer ‚Äî she shared it all.

We also spoke about Yuvraj‚Äôs journey to cricket stardom, his equation with his father Yograj Singh, her parenting style as a single mother, and for the first time, how she was introduced to her daughter-in-law Hazel Keech. It‚Äôs a candid, emotional and joyful episode you don‚Äôt want to miss!

And of course, you‚Äôll get an exclusive tour of Koca, where Yuvi takes me through his favorite dishes and the story behind launching his dream restaurant.

From the secret behind her legendary Kadhi Chawal, to Yuvraj‚Äôs most emotional cricket moments, his battle with cancer, love life with Hazel Keech and becoming a dad at 40, nothing is off the table!

snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal‚Äôs world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Dayan Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Mehwish Hayat - Ahsan Khan - Hira Mani - 21st April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Dayan is a gripping story of a girl fighting for justice after enduring a series of injustices. It follows Nihaal, a young woman whose life is shattered by a tragic turn of events.
The events that follow shake Nihaal to her core, drastically altering her personality. This leads Nihaal to embark on a journey to bring those responsible for ruining her life to justice.
Can Nihaal get the justice she deserves? Is Nihaal strong enough to take down the ones who wronged her? Can Nihaal handle everything life throws at her?

Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
